This package contains a widget for the XCenter of XWorkplace. It belongs
to the AMouse package and displays some of the current settings of the
AMouse driver.
The package contains of the following files:

XWPMouse.dll - XWorkplace Widget;
XMouNNN.hlp  - help files for widget; NNN is the language id

Just copy all files into the widget directory of XWorkplace and restart the XCenter

To change settings of AMouse with the help of this widget, try the following:
- click button 1 on mouse:  change scroll direction
- turn wheel:               change number of scroll lines
- open "properties":        displays settings page of AMouse

